1
00:00:10,177 --> 00:00:12,888
We endlessly ask ourselves.

2
00:00:15,265 --> 00:00:17,392
What is my fate?

3
00:00:19,811 --> 00:00:21,396
For thousands of years,

4
00:00:23,148 --> 00:00:27,486
the desperate quest
to see into our fate has never stopped.

5
00:00:28,487 --> 00:00:30,322
We prayed to the gods.

6
00:00:32,074 --> 00:00:34,159
We read the stars.

7
00:00:35,577 --> 00:00:36,912
We told fortunes.

8
00:00:39,498 --> 00:00:42,459
Does fate really exist?

9
00:00:43,585 --> 00:00:44,753
If it does,

10
00:00:44,836 --> 00:00:48,257
are we able to read it?

11
00:00:49,716 --> 00:00:52,594
Now, humankind's first experiment

12
00:00:53,387 --> 00:00:54,763
to answer this question

13
00:00:55,681 --> 00:00:56,723
begins.

14
00:01:01,270 --> 00:01:03,397
The fate for you to read is…

15
00:01:07,150 --> 00:01:08,652
This is the question?

16
00:01:09,528 --> 00:01:10,696
I have to win
no matter what.

17
00:01:10,779 --> 00:01:13,073
All right,
let's go all out. It's do or die.

18
00:01:13,156 --> 00:01:14,700
Granny, show me.

19
00:01:16,201 --> 00:01:20,247
Look at her eyes.

20
00:01:20,330 --> 00:01:21,498
That's the correct answer.

21
00:01:21,582 --> 00:01:22,749
Gee, it gives me the chills.

22
00:01:23,208 --> 00:01:25,294
Oh, my gosh. I have goosebumps.

23
00:01:26,169 --> 00:01:27,296
I feel nauseous.

24
00:01:29,965 --> 00:01:31,967
I'm a shaman. This is my fate.

25
00:01:32,050 --> 00:01:33,844
There's no avoiding it.

26
00:01:33,927 --> 00:01:35,470
I started seeing things.

27
00:01:35,554 --> 00:01:38,140
- I kept seeing ghosts.
- You saw ghosts?

28
00:01:38,682 --> 00:01:40,642
I'm really scared right now.

29
00:01:40,726 --> 00:01:41,852
This is so freaky.

30
00:01:42,394 --> 00:01:43,895
Watch out, Fairy! Oh, no!

31
00:01:43,979 --> 00:01:45,188
A taboo
shouldn't be broken.

32
00:01:45,272 --> 00:01:48,066
Look how angry
Granny is, you fool!

33
00:01:49,234 --> 00:01:52,904
A survival game
where those who read fate bet their own.

34
00:01:55,032 --> 00:01:57,367
Battle of Fates.

35
00:01:57,451 --> 00:02:01,621
BATTLE OF FATES

36
00:03:02,516 --> 00:03:03,725
Ow.

37
00:03:10,482 --> 00:03:11,483
This is amazing.

38
00:03:13,735 --> 00:03:14,986
I was the first to step inside.

39
00:03:15,862 --> 00:03:17,197
The moon looked great.

40
00:03:23,745 --> 00:03:29,376
This place has good energy,
with water and lakes.

41
00:03:33,713 --> 00:03:34,881
Hello.

42
00:03:34,965 --> 00:03:38,385
I'm Lady Wish,
and I'm a shaman based in Daegu.

43
00:03:39,678 --> 00:03:42,597
My family has been practicing shamanism
for 3 generations.

44
00:03:42,681 --> 00:03:46,893
My great-aunt, my father, then myself.

45
00:03:47,394 --> 00:03:51,898
I was a competitive archer
from elementary school to university.

46
00:03:51,982 --> 00:03:54,317
Jang Hyejin, the famous archer

47
00:03:54,401 --> 00:03:56,027
was my junior since elementary school.

48
00:03:56,111 --> 00:03:58,488
Archers Ki Bobae and An San

49
00:03:58,572 --> 00:04:00,532
trained with me
at Kwangju Women's University.

50
00:04:00,991 --> 00:04:02,951
Second only to archery,

51
00:04:03,034 --> 00:04:06,413
being a shaman is what I'm best at
and enjoy the most.

52
00:04:06,496 --> 00:04:10,167
It makes me feel alive, happy, and loved.

53
00:04:10,250 --> 00:04:13,753
I never got to represent Korea
as an archer,

54
00:04:13,837 --> 00:04:16,256
but as a shaman, I'm hoping to make

55
00:04:16,339 --> 00:04:19,342
a name for myself as a famous manshin.

56
00:04:35,734 --> 00:04:40,781
I bowed in all 4 directions
because spirits dwell in this place too.

57
00:04:41,490 --> 00:04:44,367
I prayed everyone would enjoy themselves

58
00:04:44,451 --> 00:04:47,204
and get through this without any mishaps.

59
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:54,961
This should be fun.

60
00:04:58,965 --> 00:05:01,802
Wow.

61
00:05:08,308 --> 00:05:09,518
I guess that's my spot.

62
00:05:17,275 --> 00:05:19,027
Hello. I'm Yoon Daeman.

63
00:05:19,110 --> 00:05:20,278
YOON DAEMAN
5-YEAR SHAMAN

64
00:05:20,362 --> 00:05:22,781
I studied and practiced Gugak

65
00:05:22,864 --> 00:05:25,325
for about 23 years.

66
00:05:25,867 --> 00:05:28,161
I mastered National Intangible
Cultural Heritage No. 57

67
00:05:28,245 --> 00:05:33,083
and Songseo Yulchang ,
Seoul Intangible Cultural Heritage No. 41.

68
00:05:33,166 --> 00:05:37,003
Still, I couldn't turn away
from my deities.

69
00:05:37,087 --> 00:05:40,090
That's why I've been a shaman ever since.

70
00:05:42,676 --> 00:05:43,760
Another male shaman.

71
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,973
Hello.

72
00:05:48,056 --> 00:05:49,599
It's Young Master Byeon.

73
00:05:50,851 --> 00:05:52,269
Hello.

74
00:05:52,352 --> 00:05:54,980
I'm Young Master Byeon,
and my shrine's in Sindang-dong.

75
00:05:55,063 --> 00:05:56,314
YOUNG MASTER BYEON
15-YEAR SHAMAN

76
00:05:56,398 --> 00:05:58,191
This is my 15th year as a shaman.

77
00:05:59,276 --> 00:06:04,531
I get a lot of entertainment agency heads
and people in show business as my clients.

78
00:06:06,992 --> 00:06:08,285
Was it Young Master Byeon?

79
00:06:08,785 --> 00:06:10,412
We're both male shamans.

80
00:06:10,495 --> 00:06:14,332
I'd say there's a slight sense
of competitiveness between us.

81
00:06:16,376 --> 00:06:17,836
Young Master Byeon?

82
00:06:17,919 --> 00:06:20,714
I thought,
"Wow, he's going to be tough to beat."

83
00:06:20,797 --> 00:06:24,301
It felt like a grandmother's spirit
is inside him.

84
00:06:33,518 --> 00:06:34,644
Hmm?

85
00:06:34,728 --> 00:06:36,438
I don't think he's a shaman.

86
00:06:36,980 --> 00:06:38,064
Hello.

87
00:06:39,065 --> 00:06:40,108
Nice to meet you.

88
00:06:40,191 --> 00:06:43,069
I'm a deputy department head
at a large company by day,

89
00:06:43,153 --> 00:06:45,113
and a corporate fortune teller by night.

90
00:06:45,196 --> 00:06:46,615
I'm Business Sage Kim.

91
00:06:47,365 --> 00:06:50,535
I've done fortune telling
for around 6,000 start-up founders

92
00:06:50,619 --> 00:06:53,455
and professionals across various fields.

93
00:06:54,289 --> 00:06:58,335
I want to show the power of Korean saju.

94
00:06:58,418 --> 00:07:00,045
- I know him.
- You do?

95
00:07:00,128 --> 00:07:01,546
He's Heoyu.

96
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:04,758
He's young,
but he has about 30 years of experience.

97
00:07:04,841 --> 00:07:08,011
I'm Heoyu, and I come from a family that's
studied myungri

98
00:07:08,094 --> 00:07:09,471
for 4 generations.

99
00:07:09,554 --> 00:07:13,642
I majored in
International Business in Washington, D.C.

100
00:07:13,725 --> 00:07:16,728
I've been doing myungri for 15 years.

101
00:07:16,811 --> 00:07:18,772
I'm Meta Myungri Joon.

102
00:07:18,855 --> 00:07:22,692
Divination has a long history,
but so does saju.

103
00:07:22,776 --> 00:07:25,528
I think we'll definitely have
the upper hand.

104
00:07:26,988 --> 00:07:30,116
I personally think
face reading beats saju.

105
00:07:32,118 --> 00:07:35,080
I'm Taeul Lee Dokyu,
and I've been reading faces for 11 years.

106
00:07:35,622 --> 00:07:37,123
- He's a face reader.
- Yes.

107
00:07:37,707 --> 00:07:38,958
He's famous in the field.

108
00:07:39,042 --> 00:07:40,251
He looks like a guru.

109
00:07:41,044 --> 00:07:42,295
I read faces,

110
00:07:42,379 --> 00:07:45,048
so I don't need any tools or a perpetual
calendar.

111
00:07:45,131 --> 00:07:49,803
The upside is, I can read a face
anytime, anywhere.

112
00:07:49,886 --> 00:07:52,222
My specialty is people's health.

113
00:07:52,305 --> 00:07:54,641
Excuse me, tarot master.

114
00:07:54,724 --> 00:07:57,394
Your kidneys are pretty weak.

115
00:07:57,477 --> 00:07:58,937
-How did you know that?
-Well…

116
00:07:59,479 --> 00:08:01,648
Your body shape says
you have weak kidneys.

117
00:08:01,731 --> 00:08:03,900
Are you a shaman?

118
00:08:03,983 --> 00:08:05,568
No, I read faces.

119
00:08:05,652 --> 00:08:08,863
You're a face reader.
Wow, so fascinating.

120
00:08:09,989 --> 00:08:12,992
I'd like to prove to everyone
that face reading

121
00:08:13,076 --> 00:08:16,287
is just as great and accurate as saju.

122
00:08:21,334 --> 00:08:23,461
Wow, what a body.

123
00:08:23,545 --> 00:08:25,714
She's gorgeous.

124
00:08:26,423 --> 00:08:28,258
Goodness.
She's like a model.

125
00:08:28,341 --> 00:08:29,926
She's beautiful.

126
00:08:40,019 --> 00:08:41,312
Wow.

127
00:08:41,396 --> 00:08:42,480
HONG YULJAE
6-YEAR SHAMAN

128
00:08:42,564 --> 00:08:43,940
She could pass
for a celebrity.

129
00:08:44,607 --> 00:08:46,526
- Hello.
- You're like a K-pop idol.

130
00:08:46,609 --> 00:08:47,944
Oh, thank you.

131
00:08:49,904 --> 00:08:52,115
Wow, this place is gorgeous.

132
00:08:52,198 --> 00:08:54,409
- She's quite flashy.
- Yes.

133
00:08:54,492 --> 00:08:56,453
-She's beautiful.
-Right.

134
00:08:56,536 --> 00:08:59,414
- Hi, hello.
- Hello.

135
00:08:59,497 --> 00:09:03,376
-I couldn't pull off those purple boots.
-That's no easy feat.

136
00:09:04,210 --> 00:09:05,837
- She looks great. Is she a celebrity?
- Wow.

137
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:11,217
I think she's a tarot master
or does astrology.

138
00:09:11,301 --> 00:09:14,554
I can't tell what those two do.

139
00:09:14,637 --> 00:09:18,016
- I believe they're shamans.
- Are they shamans?

140
00:09:18,099 --> 00:09:20,018
Lovely to meet you.

141
00:09:20,101 --> 00:09:23,063
I went from being a dancer to a shaman.

142
00:09:23,146 --> 00:09:25,899
I'm a third-year novice shaman, Seolhwa.

143
00:09:25,982 --> 00:09:29,277
I went on Dancing 9 and somehow made it
all the way to the live shows.

144
00:09:29,819 --> 00:09:34,157
But once I entered my 20s,
people started saying I'd gotten weird,

145
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,867
and the readings kept coming to me.

146
00:09:36,493 --> 00:09:39,871
That's when I realized I couldn't avoid
the calling anymore.

147
00:09:39,954 --> 00:09:45,085
I was just as serious about dance
as I am about being a shaman now.

148
00:09:45,168 --> 00:09:48,129
Walking on this path hasn't been easy.

149
00:09:48,213 --> 00:09:51,174
I want to leave this show
with my pride intact.

150
00:09:51,758 --> 00:09:53,093
Her presence…

151
00:09:55,720 --> 00:10:00,183
Gen Z shamans?
I don't get them, to be honest.

152
00:10:00,266 --> 00:10:02,018
They wear wacky clothes.

153
00:10:02,102 --> 00:10:03,436
I'm sorry to say this,

154
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:06,064
but it looks like
they're here to put on a show.

155
00:10:06,147 --> 00:10:09,109
I'm just going to
show them who I am.

156
00:10:09,192 --> 00:10:11,778
I'll just go at my own pace.

157
00:10:12,445 --> 00:10:17,033
I don't care
what the other shamans think of me.

158
00:10:17,117 --> 00:10:18,952
I just focus on my own game.

159
00:10:20,328 --> 00:10:22,372
Wow… she's got quite an aura.

160
00:10:26,084 --> 00:10:30,046
- What? Who is that?
- Huh? Who's this?

161
00:10:39,389 --> 00:10:40,390
What a presence.

162
00:10:40,473 --> 00:10:41,850
She's got amazing presence.

163
00:10:42,225 --> 00:10:43,685
Is she a tarot master?

164
00:10:45,687 --> 00:10:49,357
I've been reading tarot cards
in Sejong for 8 years.

165
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,067
I'm the god of East Asian tarot.

166
00:10:51,151 --> 00:10:53,444
I'm Monad, a tarot master.

167
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:56,447
East Asian tarot is so full of charm.

168
00:10:56,531 --> 00:11:00,702
I want more people to see
how well it fits the Korean sentiments.

169
00:11:00,785 --> 00:11:03,413
There are countless tarot traditions
around the world,

170
00:11:03,496 --> 00:11:06,666
but when it comes to Eastern tarot,
I'll be the best.

171
00:11:07,375 --> 00:11:08,459
Whoa!

172
00:11:12,338 --> 00:11:13,548
How cool.

173
00:11:14,132 --> 00:11:15,133
Incredible.

174
00:11:15,216 --> 00:11:17,343
That was a powerful entrance.

175
00:11:17,427 --> 00:11:19,179
She's definitely
the one to watch.

176
00:11:25,101 --> 00:11:26,477
-What?
-The vibe changed.

177
00:11:26,561 --> 00:11:28,938
- What's this music?
- Is the final boss coming?

178
00:11:31,024 --> 00:11:33,109
What's going on?

179
00:11:34,194 --> 00:11:36,112
- Wow.
- That's cool.

180
00:11:36,779 --> 00:11:39,240
How impressive.

181
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,076
A grand entrance.

182
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:43,453
Bringing in good energy.

183
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:48,166
Awesome!

184
00:11:48,666 --> 00:11:50,710
I'm blown away.

185
00:11:51,294 --> 00:11:53,129
I'm Ineuidang, the shaman

186
00:11:53,213 --> 00:11:56,257
who foresaw
the December 2024 martial law crisis.

187
00:11:56,341 --> 00:11:57,467
INEUIDANG
SHAMAN

188
00:11:58,635 --> 00:12:02,513
The spirits of independence fighters took
me over and urged me to go to Yeouido,

189
00:12:03,264 --> 00:12:05,058
warning me
that the country was in danger.

190
00:12:05,808 --> 00:12:09,187
They told me to beat my drum
as if I were going to war.

191
00:12:10,730 --> 00:12:14,484
I beat my drum hard
outside the National Assembly building.

192
00:12:15,151 --> 00:12:16,361
I will survive

193
00:12:17,612 --> 00:12:20,240
with the same intensity I had
when I predicted the martial law crisis.

194
00:12:22,992 --> 00:12:24,118
She's got real presence.

195
00:12:27,538 --> 00:12:29,666
- A drum says it all.
- Yes.

196
00:12:29,749 --> 00:12:30,792
I like it.

197
00:12:38,049 --> 00:12:39,050
Who's that?

198
00:12:39,842 --> 00:12:40,843
Who?

199
00:12:41,386 --> 00:12:43,763
- A celebrity?
- A comedian?

200
00:12:44,264 --> 00:12:47,183
Hello. Oh, hi!

201
00:12:48,101 --> 00:12:50,353
- No way!
- Hello.

202
00:12:50,436 --> 00:12:52,105
-Hello.
-Gosh.

203
00:12:52,188 --> 00:12:54,607
-Hello.
-It's… It's Lee Kookjoo!

204
00:12:54,691 --> 00:12:56,109
-Hello.
-Whoa, it's her!

205
00:12:56,192 --> 00:12:57,527
Wow!

206
00:12:57,610 --> 00:12:59,112
What's she doing here?

207
00:12:59,195 --> 00:13:01,823
-Hello.
-It's Lee Kookjoo.

208
00:13:01,906 --> 00:13:03,950
Is she here to get a reading?

209
00:13:04,033 --> 00:13:07,370
- I don't know. Hang on.
- Is she a host? A client?

210
00:13:08,663 --> 00:13:10,123
I think she's a contestant.

211
00:13:10,206 --> 00:13:11,582
Wow!

212
00:13:11,666 --> 00:13:14,085
-Yes, I'm here as a contestant.
-Goodness.

213
00:13:14,168 --> 00:13:16,296
- What a shocker.
- I do tarot reading.

214
00:13:17,505 --> 00:13:19,215
- I'm not possessed.
- "NOT possessed," she says.

215
00:13:19,299 --> 00:13:21,718
-I'm not a shaman.
-She's not possessed.

216
00:13:21,801 --> 00:13:23,219
How long have you been doing tarot?

217
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:25,722
I've been doing it for 5 years.

218
00:13:25,805 --> 00:13:27,473
An unexpected contestant.

219
00:13:27,557 --> 00:13:29,350
He looks pretty hip.

220
00:13:30,101 --> 00:13:31,311
I'm getting tarot vibes.

221
00:13:31,394 --> 00:13:34,188
His older sister is a celebrity.

222
00:13:34,272 --> 00:13:36,065
I'm Beentarot, a tarot master.

223
00:13:36,149 --> 00:13:39,694
Actress Yoon Gai is my older sister.

224
00:13:39,777 --> 00:13:42,405
I do tarot readings for her
before she starts

225
00:13:42,488 --> 00:13:45,033
a new show or something big.

226
00:13:45,116 --> 00:13:47,410
We're a big support to each other.

227
00:13:48,327 --> 00:13:49,328
Hello.

228
00:13:49,412 --> 00:13:53,458
Hello, I'm Choi Hannah.
This is my third year as a tarot master.

229
00:13:53,541 --> 00:13:57,378
I was on Possessed Love last year.

230
00:13:58,129 --> 00:14:02,967
Spiritual tarot requires you
to read the energy shift in the moment,

231
00:14:03,051 --> 00:14:05,553
which allows you to see more details.

232
00:14:06,054 --> 00:14:08,681
Everyone's so different.

233
00:14:09,265 --> 00:14:10,892
How did they gather all these people?

234
00:14:12,810 --> 00:14:14,854
Hello. I'm Sage Cheonmyeong,

235
00:14:14,937 --> 00:14:18,066
and I did my PhD at KAIST
before becoming a shaman.

236
00:14:18,649 --> 00:14:22,153
I'm Hyeondo, and I do Religious Studies
at Seoul National University.

237
00:14:22,236 --> 00:14:26,157
I did my undergraduate at Korea University
and masters at Seoul National University.

238
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:28,701
I'm pretty sure I can win easily.

239
00:14:28,785 --> 00:14:31,496
-They seem really professional.
-Yes, so professional.

240
00:14:31,579 --> 00:14:32,580
I know.

241
00:14:36,834 --> 00:14:38,711
- That's a Fairy.
- Hello, Fairy!

242
00:14:40,129 --> 00:14:42,131
-She's like an angel.
-Is she a princess?

243
00:14:42,215 --> 00:14:44,300
We have a Heavenly Fairy.

244
00:14:45,843 --> 00:14:47,303
Gosh, so cute.

245
00:14:49,180 --> 00:14:51,015
- She's a baby.
- She's playing peekaboo.

246
00:14:51,099 --> 00:14:53,059
How old are you, Fairy?

247
00:14:53,142 --> 00:14:54,769
- I'm 5.
- You're 5 years old?

248
00:14:54,852 --> 00:14:56,229
- Adorable.
- She's a Baby Fairy.

249
00:14:56,312 --> 00:14:58,064
- That's so cute.
- Smart girl.

250
00:14:58,940 --> 00:15:00,691
How cute. What a pretty fan.

251
00:15:01,567 --> 00:15:02,902
She's a baby.

252
00:15:02,985 --> 00:15:05,822
I'm 29 years old,

253
00:15:05,905 --> 00:15:09,408
and this is my 26th year as a shaman.

254
00:15:09,492 --> 00:15:11,202
I'm Kwon Sujin, a manshin.

255
00:15:12,078 --> 00:15:14,872
I started telling fortunes
as soon as I could speak.

256
00:15:14,956 --> 00:15:16,958
That was when I was 4.

257
00:15:17,041 --> 00:15:20,628
I had a pure soul as a child,
and I lived on a mountain,

258
00:15:20,711 --> 00:15:23,131
so I started feeling the spirits early on.

259
00:15:23,214 --> 00:15:27,343
I bet of all the shamans here today,
I've been a shaman the longest.

260
00:15:27,426 --> 00:15:31,639
I have a lot of experience,
and I hold the title of a manshin.

261
00:15:31,722 --> 00:15:34,934
I'll just be myself and perform
in a way that suits that title.

262
00:15:35,017 --> 00:15:39,480
I believe in my deities,
so I don't doubt my readings.

263
00:15:44,610 --> 00:15:45,611
Gosh.

264
00:15:45,695 --> 00:15:47,363
They're wearing hanbok.

265
00:15:47,446 --> 00:15:50,158
Who's that? Is it a woman?

266
00:15:50,741 --> 00:15:52,118
Is that a man or a woman?

267
00:15:55,288 --> 00:15:56,664
Gosh. Hang on.

268
00:15:56,747 --> 00:15:58,416
- Is it a man?
- Wait, what?

269
00:15:58,499 --> 00:15:59,750
Oh, my word.

270
00:16:00,376 --> 00:16:02,086
-Hello.
-Welcome.

271
00:16:02,170 --> 00:16:03,504
He's dressed like a Granny.

272
00:16:04,422 --> 00:16:06,549
-He's wearing a woman's hanbok.
-How extraordinary.

273
00:16:07,049 --> 00:16:08,926
-He's a man, right?
-Yes.

274
00:16:09,010 --> 00:16:10,344
What a beautiful hanbok.

275
00:16:10,428 --> 00:16:12,138
Looks like a female spirit possessed him.

276
00:16:13,139 --> 00:16:15,766
Do male shamans
wear a woman's hanbok

277
00:16:15,850 --> 00:16:18,060
if they're possessed by a female deity?

278
00:16:18,144 --> 00:16:20,646
I guess they do what their deity
tells them to.

279
00:16:20,730 --> 00:16:24,025
My goodness.
Look at how he walks. So sassy.

280
00:16:24,567 --> 00:16:25,776
Hello.

281
00:16:27,069 --> 00:16:29,780
Whoa,
what an incredible presence.

282
00:16:32,158 --> 00:16:34,202
The Granny got up there all tough.

283
00:16:34,994 --> 00:16:36,829
He looks so confident.

284
00:16:38,873 --> 00:16:41,334
I'm pretty sure
he's not even 20 years old yet.

285
00:16:41,417 --> 00:16:42,752
For real?

286
00:16:42,835 --> 00:16:44,212
He's young.

287
00:16:45,963 --> 00:16:50,134
I heard I'm the youngest one here.
I'm Young Master Jiseon, and I'm 18.

288
00:16:50,218 --> 00:16:52,887
I started out when I was 5 years old.

289
00:16:53,888 --> 00:16:56,849
I first stood on a jakdu
when I was 8 or 9 years old.

290
00:16:58,100 --> 00:17:01,395
The General spirits
allow me to stand on the blades

291
00:17:01,479 --> 00:17:03,731
to suppress
the negative energy or misfortune.

292
00:17:03,814 --> 00:17:06,442
I feel great
when the General spirit takes me over.

293
00:17:06,525 --> 00:17:07,944
The General will protect you.

294
00:17:09,237 --> 00:17:12,406
I've reached a certain level
over the past 13 years.

295
00:17:12,490 --> 00:17:14,617
I'll prove that when it comes
to spiritual divination,

296
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:17,495
I have more experience
and better skills than most.

297
00:17:17,578 --> 00:17:19,247
I'm going to win this thing.

298
00:17:19,956 --> 00:17:21,290
Let the youngest show you what he's got.

299
00:17:23,251 --> 00:17:24,377
-You're young.
-Yes.

300
00:17:24,460 --> 00:17:27,630
I started as a kid too.
I became a shaman when I was 5.

301
00:17:29,215 --> 00:17:32,760
Your soul is still clear even though
you've done this for a long time.

302
00:17:32,843 --> 00:17:34,887
-Me? Thank you.
-Yes.

303
00:17:34,971 --> 00:17:36,973
We've got a lot of strong contenders here.

304
00:17:37,056 --> 00:17:40,851
One glance, and I can tell
they're tough to beat. Oh, no.

305
00:17:42,436 --> 00:17:43,437
Someone's coming.

306
00:17:44,605 --> 00:17:46,941
Here comes the Fairy!

307
00:17:48,359 --> 00:17:50,486
-Gosh.
-She's flashy too.

308
00:17:51,404 --> 00:17:54,657
No way. Wow.

309
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:57,410
-Here comes the Fairy!
-Hello!

310
00:17:57,994 --> 00:18:01,497
I'm Soho, and I want to be the star
of the shaman world!

311
00:18:01,581 --> 00:18:02,957
-Hello, everyone!
-You look great!

312
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:05,293
Good vibes your way!
The spring wind's here.

313
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:07,503
Here's some good fortune!

314
00:18:08,045 --> 00:18:11,215
- Here goes good fortune!
- Yes, please.

315
00:18:11,299 --> 00:18:13,301
Take the luck!

316
00:18:13,384 --> 00:18:14,760
Watch out for the water.

317
00:18:14,844 --> 00:18:17,555
-Good fortune. Oh, she might fall.
-Watch out.

318
00:18:18,055 --> 00:18:19,473
Good fortune for you!

319
00:18:20,099 --> 00:18:21,475
You're so pretty, Fairy.

320
00:18:21,559 --> 00:18:22,852
Nice to meet you.

321
00:18:22,935 --> 00:18:24,937
Watch out, Fairy! Oh, I knew it.

322
00:18:25,021 --> 00:18:27,064
- Nice to meet you.
- Watch out, Fairy!

323
00:18:27,148 --> 00:18:29,650
Oh, I knew it. Gosh, are you okay?

324
00:18:29,734 --> 00:18:32,153
-Oh, dear.
-Oh, I knew it. Gosh, are you okay?

325
00:18:32,236 --> 00:18:34,405
-Oh, dear.
-Oh, no.

326
00:18:34,488 --> 00:18:36,198
The water…

327
00:18:36,282 --> 00:18:38,618
Oh, dear.

328
00:18:39,869 --> 00:18:41,579
-This is precious to you, right?
-Be careful.

329
00:18:41,662 --> 00:18:42,955
My crystal ball!

330
00:18:43,039 --> 00:18:45,458
-Oh, dear.
-She fell in the water.

331
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:48,294
-It's okay. It's happened to my girl too.
-Are you okay?

332
00:18:48,377 --> 00:18:49,879
The Fairy tripped.

333
00:18:49,962 --> 00:18:51,589
I'm okay, everyone!

334
00:18:51,672 --> 00:18:53,007
Give me a warm welcome!

335
00:18:55,968 --> 00:18:57,720
It happens to 4-year-olds!

336
00:18:57,803 --> 00:19:00,014
-I'm fine!
-You're 4. It's okay.

337
00:19:00,097 --> 00:19:02,141
- She's fine.
- I love her energy.

338
00:19:02,683 --> 00:19:04,644
-She's so upbeat.
-Yes.

339
00:19:04,727 --> 00:19:07,897
- I'm a novice, so I'm full of energy.
- I can see that.

340
00:19:07,980 --> 00:19:09,273
Is she with a Child spirit?

341
00:19:11,359 --> 00:19:14,528
-I fell in there while blowing kisses.
-You did?

342
00:19:14,612 --> 00:19:16,072
Maybe because she's
from the Dragon Palace.

343
00:19:16,155 --> 00:19:17,740
She serves the Dragon King?

344
00:19:18,282 --> 00:19:19,950
We have a Fairy get-together here.

345
00:19:20,493 --> 00:19:22,495
-We are the world.
-Watch over them, Granny.

346
00:19:22,578 --> 00:19:23,621
SOHO, LITTLE MISS HWARANG

347
00:19:23,704 --> 00:19:25,373
- I envy them.
- How pretty. I'm jealous.

348
00:19:25,456 --> 00:19:27,291
I'd love to have that youthfulness.

349
00:19:27,375 --> 00:19:29,627
-They're novices.
-Exactly. How great is that?

350
00:19:29,710 --> 00:19:32,254
They look sweet and cute
whatever they do.

351
00:19:32,338 --> 00:19:34,423
Not us. We're jaded.

352
00:19:35,424 --> 00:19:37,259
- They're all our rivals.
- You're right.

353
00:19:44,892 --> 00:19:47,520
- Hello.
- Hello.

354
00:19:47,603 --> 00:19:49,689
Hello.

355
00:19:49,772 --> 00:19:51,607
Oh, it's him!

356
00:19:52,108 --> 00:19:55,277
Didn't he become famous
for crazy spiritual powers?

357
00:19:56,112 --> 00:19:58,155
- He's no joke.
- You look splendid.

358
00:19:58,239 --> 00:20:01,075
- A lot of familiar faces.
- Everyone seems to know him.

359
00:20:02,743 --> 00:20:04,829
He brought
his instruments in an Hermès bag.

360
00:20:05,496 --> 00:20:06,997
Wow, a rich man.

361
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:11,627
I'm Young Master Byeolsang,
and I'm a Hwanghae-do manshin of 11 years.

362
00:20:11,711 --> 00:20:15,005
I worked as a hairstylist from 9th grade

363
00:20:15,089 --> 00:20:16,632
until I was 25.

364
00:20:16,716 --> 00:20:19,468
My first reading was for my mom,

365
00:20:19,552 --> 00:20:21,762
and soon after, I became a shaman.

366
00:20:21,846 --> 00:20:26,142
Since then, I've been making
about 100 million won every month.

367
00:20:26,684 --> 00:20:28,436
-You're here too.
-Hi, my man.

368
00:20:28,519 --> 00:20:30,187
-Hello.
-Welcome.

369
00:20:31,856 --> 00:20:33,733
-Nice to meet you.
-Hello.

370
00:20:33,816 --> 00:20:36,902
Guess shamans have
gear buffs too.

371
00:20:36,986 --> 00:20:40,364
- Look at that bag.
- Isn't that really expensive?

372
00:20:40,448 --> 00:20:43,701
He's probably
the richest one here. Definitely loaded.

373
00:20:44,285 --> 00:20:46,620
Young Master Byeolsang does
North Korean rites.

374
00:20:46,704 --> 00:20:48,914
Among those in our age group,
he's unrivaled,

375
00:20:48,998 --> 00:20:51,083
and people tend to compare us.

376
00:20:51,167 --> 00:20:55,421
He's powerful, charismatic, almost like
a general with a dark presence.

377
00:20:55,504 --> 00:20:57,506
But I do Hanyang-style rites.

378
00:20:57,590 --> 00:20:59,550
I wear white and channel an old lady.

379
00:21:00,176 --> 00:21:03,554
We've been friendly rivals for years.

380
00:21:03,637 --> 00:21:05,514
I should beat him at least.

381
00:21:05,598 --> 00:21:07,892
I have to beat that punk.

382
00:21:07,975 --> 00:21:11,103
Hwanghae-do rites are
rough and flashy.

383
00:21:11,771 --> 00:21:15,316
It's like a battle zone.
We use blades from start to finish.

384
00:21:15,399 --> 00:21:17,026
About 600 people attended

385
00:21:17,109 --> 00:21:19,320
my New Harvest Prayer Ritual last year.

386
00:21:19,403 --> 00:21:22,907
The rite cost about 100 million won,

387
00:21:22,990 --> 00:21:24,617
but I made many times that.

388
00:21:25,117 --> 00:21:27,411
That shows how powerful my deities are.

389
00:21:28,204 --> 00:21:31,707
I'm confident I can take on
whoever challenges me.

390
00:21:33,709 --> 00:21:35,795
All the famous shamans are here.

391
00:21:36,921 --> 00:21:38,672
I sense some strong energy.

392
00:21:39,298 --> 00:21:40,341
Very strong.

393
00:21:40,424 --> 00:21:43,385
Oh, one of the elders.

394
00:21:43,469 --> 00:21:44,762
Oh, gee.

395
00:21:44,845 --> 00:21:46,013
It's very powerful.

396
00:21:47,223 --> 00:21:49,225
- Wow.
- I love this kind of thing.

397
00:21:49,767 --> 00:21:50,768
What's that?

398
00:21:51,352 --> 00:21:52,520
That's fascinating.

399
00:21:52,603 --> 00:21:55,105
- What are those? Radio antennas?
- Water dowsing.

400
00:21:55,189 --> 00:21:56,941
Isn't that a feng shui thing?

401
00:21:57,024 --> 00:21:59,443
It's gauging
our spiritual powers.

402
00:21:59,527 --> 00:22:01,987
This is the old-school stuff.

403
00:22:02,071 --> 00:22:05,241
- It's retro.
- Yes, retro.

404
00:22:05,324 --> 00:22:06,659
I'm Kim Baekmun,

405
00:22:06,742 --> 00:22:09,078
and I've studied
fortune telling and foot reading

406
00:22:09,161 --> 00:22:10,830
for over 30 years.

407
00:22:10,913 --> 00:22:12,456
KIM BAEKMUN
35-YEAR FOOT READER

408
00:22:12,540 --> 00:22:14,250
I specialize in foot reading.

409
00:22:14,333 --> 00:22:16,210
I also study Qimen Dunjia
,

410
00:22:16,293 --> 00:22:18,128
myungri, the Book of Changes,

411
00:22:18,212 --> 00:22:21,507
Hexagram Divination, crystal gazing,
and gemstone divination.

412
00:22:23,133 --> 00:22:25,719
I can also do water dowsing.

413
00:22:27,930 --> 00:22:31,308
- It's him.
- Do you know him?

414
00:22:31,392 --> 00:22:34,186
He created the saju reading software.

415
00:22:34,562 --> 00:22:36,105
I use it too.

416
00:22:36,188 --> 00:22:38,482
- He's really famous.
- I see.

417
00:22:38,566 --> 00:22:40,901
See if you've got a good spot.

418
00:22:40,985 --> 00:22:42,486
Is that a good spot?

419
00:22:42,570 --> 00:22:45,239
The water vein must be no joke here.
There's water everywhere.

420
00:22:46,198 --> 00:22:47,241
Nice to meet you.

421
00:22:47,324 --> 00:22:50,870
The energy is… Gosh, it's really strong.

422
00:22:52,204 --> 00:22:55,958
- The antennas are going crazy.
- They're going wild.

423
00:22:56,041 --> 00:22:59,336
- Oh, my goodness. Look at that.
- It's moving nonstop.

424
00:22:59,420 --> 00:23:00,421
They won't stop.

425
00:23:00,504 --> 00:23:01,714
That looks powerful.

426
00:23:01,797 --> 00:23:03,591
Everyone here has
some powerful energy.

427
00:23:05,092 --> 00:23:07,678
This place must have good energy.

428
00:23:07,761 --> 00:23:09,263
There's a lot of water energy here.

429
00:23:10,472 --> 00:23:12,308
I see a lot of big names here.

430
00:23:12,391 --> 00:23:14,059
Ryu Donghak?

431
00:23:14,143 --> 00:23:16,395
All he does is study myungri.

432
00:23:16,478 --> 00:23:18,898
He has his own knowledge and expertise.

433
00:23:19,523 --> 00:23:22,192
We have a master in our midst.

434
00:23:22,276 --> 00:23:25,112
But the win is still mine.

435
00:23:25,821 --> 00:23:26,822
Wish me luck.

436
00:23:28,324 --> 00:23:30,576
The entrances keep
getting grander.

437
00:23:32,202 --> 00:23:33,662
Hello.

438
00:23:33,746 --> 00:23:35,706
Welcome.

439
00:23:36,332 --> 00:23:38,417
- Nice to meet you.
- Hello.

440
00:23:38,500 --> 00:23:40,461
-He's handsome!
-Hello.

441
00:23:41,337 --> 00:23:42,338
Who's that?

442
00:23:43,797 --> 00:23:44,798
Who is he?

443
00:23:45,758 --> 00:23:47,259
Who? Who's that?

444
00:23:47,343 --> 00:23:50,846
Hwarang, we've never met anyone
handsome on our prayer trail,

445
00:23:50,930 --> 00:23:52,264
and now they're all here.

446
00:23:52,348 --> 00:23:54,183
It's full
of good-looking people.

447
00:23:55,809 --> 00:23:58,270
-I've never met anyone handsome.
-Right?

448
00:23:58,354 --> 00:24:00,689
- He's the first cute male shaman.
- Yes.

449
00:24:01,315 --> 00:24:02,733
Hello.

450
00:24:02,816 --> 00:24:05,569
I'm Young Master Plum Blossom from Mokpo.

451
00:24:06,070 --> 00:24:08,656
My shaman family
does a lot of tough rites.

452
00:24:09,823 --> 00:24:14,203
We're called the Avengers because we
pull off even the hardest rites.

453
00:24:14,787 --> 00:24:16,246
My goal is

454
00:24:16,330 --> 00:24:20,918
to be the best male shaman
among the 49 contestants.

455
00:24:21,543 --> 00:24:23,671
The shamans are
all pretty young.

456
00:24:23,754 --> 00:24:25,089
They're all young
and good-looking.

457
00:24:25,172 --> 00:24:27,508
Yes, they're cuties.

458
00:24:27,591 --> 00:24:30,427
- Hey, he looks cool.
- It's like a scene from a K-drama.

459
00:24:30,511 --> 00:24:34,306
- Oh, wow.
- Everyone's so handsome.

460
00:24:35,307 --> 00:24:38,143
That shaman.
He's a stunner.

461
00:24:38,227 --> 00:24:41,855
How cute.
He's like a little boy.

462
00:24:41,939 --> 00:24:44,525
They gathered
the young male shamans from all over.

463
00:24:44,608 --> 00:24:46,193
Right?

464
00:24:47,319 --> 00:24:48,320
Who's that?

465
00:24:48,404 --> 00:24:50,990
He's dressed in white.

466
00:24:51,740 --> 00:24:53,450
A handsome young man is walking in.

467
00:24:53,534 --> 00:24:55,744
What? He's really tall.

468
00:24:56,412 --> 00:24:59,415
- He's so tall.
- He's like a model.

469
00:25:00,416 --> 00:25:02,084
Wait, what?

470
00:25:04,878 --> 00:25:08,257
- I've seen him somewhere.
- Hey, it's him.

471
00:25:08,340 --> 00:25:11,552
- He's from Possessed Love.
- He was on Possessed Love.

472
00:25:11,635 --> 00:25:14,847
- Possessed Love!
- Oh, Possessed Love?

473
00:25:15,139 --> 00:25:16,140
CHEONHAE HWASIN
2-YEAR SHAMAN

474
00:25:16,223 --> 00:25:17,933
He's like a knight in shining armor.

475
00:25:18,017 --> 00:25:19,518
He's so handsome.

476
00:25:19,601 --> 00:25:21,645
- Hongjo.
- Hello.

477
00:25:21,729 --> 00:25:23,689
- Hey.
- Hongjo.

478
00:25:24,189 --> 00:25:25,858
Gosh.

479
00:25:25,941 --> 00:25:28,193
- You're right next to me, too.
- Right, I am.

480
00:25:28,277 --> 00:25:29,486
What's happening?

481
00:25:29,570 --> 00:25:32,740
-Why are you next to me?
-I don't know. Did they intend it?

482
00:25:32,823 --> 00:25:36,493
There was someone
I was on another show with.

483
00:25:37,244 --> 00:25:39,538
I didn't think I'd see her here.

484
00:25:43,667 --> 00:25:46,128
Oh, what? Is that a box?

485
00:25:46,211 --> 00:25:47,671
- He's wearing a box.
- Box Man?

486
00:25:48,839 --> 00:25:51,759
Is that a microwave
over his head?

487
00:25:51,842 --> 00:25:55,179
It's a television.

488
00:26:03,228 --> 00:26:04,229
TV Man.

489
00:26:06,732 --> 00:26:08,734
That's incredible.

490
00:26:10,069 --> 00:26:13,113
- Retro Man. Hello.
- Hello.

491
00:26:13,197 --> 00:26:14,198
Nice to meet you.

492
00:26:14,281 --> 00:26:16,617
- Hello.
- I'm a male shaman.

493
00:26:16,700 --> 00:26:20,662
- Can you see?
- How does he see?

494
00:26:20,746 --> 00:26:22,331
He found his spot just fine.

495
00:26:22,831 --> 00:26:24,166
Is that a real TV?

496
00:26:24,249 --> 00:26:25,709
Yes, I bought it
at Dongmyo flea market.

497
00:26:25,793 --> 00:26:26,794
Oh.

498
00:26:26,877 --> 00:26:28,545
There are
many great fortune tellers here,

499
00:26:28,629 --> 00:26:30,380
but I'm the only one wearing a TV?

500
00:26:30,464 --> 00:26:33,342
- It's like King of Masked Singer.
- Exactly.

501
00:26:33,425 --> 00:26:35,094
The King of Masked Singer zone.

502
00:26:35,177 --> 00:26:36,929
MASKED TAROT,
YOUNG MASTER CHERRY BLOSSOM

503
00:26:37,012 --> 00:26:39,807
- Everyone's so unique.
- I know, right?

504
00:26:39,890 --> 00:26:43,519
- Everyone's so different.
- That's right.

505
00:26:44,686 --> 00:26:46,355
I've never seen anyone use that before.

506
00:26:46,980 --> 00:26:49,608
I'm Polaris, a conjurer.

507
00:26:50,818 --> 00:26:52,903
I'm Juno, and I can tell everything

508
00:26:52,986 --> 00:26:55,322
about someone from their name.

509
00:26:55,906 --> 00:26:57,825
I'm shaman Doeyu,

510
00:26:57,908 --> 00:26:59,701
and I used to be a K-pop idol trainee.

511
00:26:59,785 --> 00:27:01,036
DOEYU
IDOL TRAINEE-TURNED-SHAMAN

512
00:27:01,120 --> 00:27:02,788
She's from North Korea.

513
00:27:02,871 --> 00:27:05,582
- Oh, like actually North Korean?
- Yes, she's from North Korea.

514
00:27:05,666 --> 00:27:08,502
Isn't she the figure skater-turned-shaman?

515
00:27:08,585 --> 00:27:10,045
The figure skater shaman!

516
00:27:10,129 --> 00:27:12,047
She kept seeing ghosts
at the ice rink

517
00:27:12,131 --> 00:27:13,632
- Really?
- and became a shaman.

518
00:27:15,092 --> 00:27:16,969
- How tall!
- Is she a model?

519
00:27:17,052 --> 00:27:18,137
She looks like an elf.

520
00:27:20,848 --> 00:27:23,725
She's a famous transgender shaman.

521
00:27:23,809 --> 00:27:26,061
We've got
the most famous people in Korea.

522
00:27:27,145 --> 00:27:28,730
Is this the last person?

523
00:27:29,398 --> 00:27:33,151
The last contestant.
I wonder how powerful their energy is.

524
00:27:34,403 --> 00:27:36,071
Gosh, who could it be?

525
00:27:36,154 --> 00:27:38,907
- She looks graceful in a hanbok.
- Yes, she has a nice silhouette.

526
00:27:47,708 --> 00:27:50,294
Hey,
that person's really famous.

527
00:27:50,377 --> 00:27:53,714
It's her! The young shaman
who foresaw MC Mong's future.

528
00:27:53,797 --> 00:27:57,175
-When she was a child. MC Mong.
-Yeah, predicted what happened to MC Mong.

529
00:27:57,259 --> 00:27:59,386
MC Mong!

530
00:27:59,469 --> 00:28:01,680
- Isn't she really famous?
- She's all grown up.

531
00:28:01,763 --> 00:28:03,348
She became a shaman at a young age.

532
00:28:03,432 --> 00:28:05,851
- Oh, really?
- The child shaman on Star King.

533
00:28:05,934 --> 00:28:07,352
- For real?
- Yes.

534
00:28:08,103 --> 00:28:11,148
- Her aura is no joke.
- She's done this for long.

535
00:28:11,231 --> 00:28:13,609
Young in age,
but rich in experience.

536
00:28:13,692 --> 00:28:16,194
- Definitely.
- Hello, little miss!

537
00:28:16,278 --> 00:28:19,156
She may be a little miss, but there's
an old Granny spirit inside her.

538
00:28:19,239 --> 00:28:21,325
An old Granny's in there.

539
00:28:22,200 --> 00:28:23,952
How old are you now?

540
00:28:24,036 --> 00:28:25,245
I'm 26.

541
00:28:26,330 --> 00:28:29,124
My shrine is in Ansan, Gyeonggi-do.

542
00:28:29,207 --> 00:28:31,960
I'm Lee Sobin, a shaman.
I'm pleased to meet you.

543
00:28:32,461 --> 00:28:36,798
I became a shaman when I was 7.

544
00:28:37,758 --> 00:28:39,718
That's when I was spiritually called.

545
00:28:40,677 --> 00:28:43,722
I appeared on TV when I was 9

546
00:28:43,805 --> 00:28:45,349
