547
00:28:45,933 --> 00:28:48,143
FORETELLING OF MC MONG'S MISDEED
SENT CHILLS DOWN THE SPINE

548
00:28:48,226 --> 00:28:50,437
STAR KING CHILD SHAMAN'S
ACCURATE PROPHECY

549
00:28:50,520 --> 00:28:52,105
My Granny spirit said

550
00:28:52,189 --> 00:28:55,442
as long as I believe in my deities
and speak truthfully, like I used to,

551
00:28:55,525 --> 00:28:57,402
it will work out.

552
00:28:57,903 --> 00:28:59,613
If I put my faith in her,

553
00:28:59,696 --> 00:29:01,740
I think I can win it all.

554
00:29:03,116 --> 00:29:04,910
Total respect.

555
00:29:04,993 --> 00:29:08,789
For me, Sobin was
the most intimidating shaman of all.

556
00:29:08,872 --> 00:29:11,750
I said I thought she'd win.

557
00:29:11,833 --> 00:29:13,585
She's here too.

558
00:29:14,753 --> 00:29:17,130
Manshin Lee Sobin.

559
00:29:17,214 --> 00:29:18,799
I felt a connection with her.

560
00:29:18,882 --> 00:29:21,259
But I do want to beat her, of course.

561
00:29:21,927 --> 00:29:25,639
Lee Sobin's spiritually clear.

562
00:29:25,722 --> 00:29:27,015
Lee Sobin.

563
00:29:27,099 --> 00:29:28,517
Lee Sobin.

564
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:30,018
Lee Sobin.

565
00:29:30,102 --> 00:29:31,895
- Lee Sobin.
- Lee Sobin.

566
00:29:31,979 --> 00:29:33,021
Lee Sobin, was it?

567
00:29:33,105 --> 00:29:34,481
- Lee Sobin.
- Lee Sobin.

568
00:29:34,564 --> 00:29:36,525
She's a strong contender to win.

569
00:29:38,193 --> 00:29:41,363
This show really pulled out
all the stops.

570
00:29:42,239 --> 00:29:43,865
It's a battle of the gods.

571
00:29:44,992 --> 00:29:46,618
A battle of the gods.

572
00:29:47,869 --> 00:29:49,538
Is everyone here?

573
00:29:50,330 --> 00:29:51,581
Is this all?

574
00:29:52,624 --> 00:29:55,836
What's happening?

575
00:30:00,424 --> 00:30:02,884
Gosh. What's this?

576
00:30:02,968 --> 00:30:04,594
It's mesmerizing.

577
00:30:06,430 --> 00:30:07,764
Impressive.

578
00:30:12,310 --> 00:30:14,771
It feels like
a whole new world is opening up.

579
00:30:16,732 --> 00:30:19,901
Welcome to Battle of Fates.

580
00:30:20,402 --> 00:30:23,238
I feel nervous.
I didn't until yesterday.

581
00:30:23,321 --> 00:30:24,698
I'm so nervous.

582
00:30:25,741 --> 00:30:26,742
I'm shaking.

583
00:30:27,951 --> 00:30:29,786
Gathered here are

584
00:30:29,870 --> 00:30:31,413
saju experts,

585
00:30:31,496 --> 00:30:32,789
tarot masters,

586
00:30:32,873 --> 00:30:33,957
shamans,

587
00:30:34,041 --> 00:30:35,083
face readers,

588
00:30:35,167 --> 00:30:36,752
foot readers, and so on.

589
00:30:36,835 --> 00:30:39,546
The 49 Fate Readers

590
00:30:40,172 --> 00:30:43,925
use their own unique gifts
to tell fortunes.

591
00:30:44,009 --> 00:30:45,886
Mmm, "Fate Readers."

592
00:30:46,470 --> 00:30:48,638
Some use the power of deities.

593
00:30:48,722 --> 00:30:51,683
Some use spiritual sense and intuition.

594
00:30:52,559 --> 00:30:57,189
Only those who see through fate
will survive Battle of Fates.

595
00:30:58,899 --> 00:31:03,195
The last one to survive this battle

596
00:31:04,237 --> 00:31:06,406
will become the final Fate Reader

597
00:31:06,490 --> 00:31:10,452
and win 100 million won in prize money.

598
00:31:11,953 --> 00:31:12,996
Let's do this!

599
00:31:15,332 --> 00:31:17,626
- 100 million? That's crazy.
- No way.

600
00:31:19,795 --> 00:31:21,546
I think I'll win.

601
00:31:23,215 --> 00:31:24,716
I think I'll be
the final winner.

602
00:31:25,217 --> 00:31:27,761
Who's most likely to win? Obviously me.

603
00:31:27,844 --> 00:31:29,679
You're all beneath me.

604
00:31:29,763 --> 00:31:31,306
I'm going to win.

605
00:31:32,724 --> 00:31:34,893
Isn't this a showdown
between shamans?

606
00:31:34,976 --> 00:31:38,146
Only a shaman stands a chance.

607
00:31:38,855 --> 00:31:42,943
They did kind of get on my nerves.

608
00:31:43,026 --> 00:31:46,029
Tarot readings are often
more accurate than spiritual divination.

609
00:31:46,113 --> 00:31:48,949
Tarot masters have
a tougher shot than saju experts.

610
00:31:51,368 --> 00:31:53,370
When a shaman sees another shaman…

611
00:31:54,663 --> 00:31:57,207
We just know whether
we can beat the other person.

612
00:31:57,290 --> 00:31:59,626
So it begins.

613
00:31:59,709 --> 00:32:01,711
A battle of the gods.

614
00:32:02,337 --> 00:32:04,089
I'm going to win this battle.

615
00:32:05,674 --> 00:32:08,760
It's coming down.

616
00:32:09,469 --> 00:32:11,847
- It's coming down. What is that?
- It's scary.

617
00:32:11,930 --> 00:32:13,431
I'm scared all of a sudden.

618
00:32:16,685 --> 00:32:18,979
Dear 49 Fate Readers.

619
00:32:20,564 --> 00:32:22,440
Before going into battle,

620
00:32:22,524 --> 00:32:26,111
offer your prayers
and blessings to the moon.

621
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:45,672
You may begin your prayers now.

622
00:33:03,648 --> 00:33:05,609
It was so scary.

623
00:33:06,818 --> 00:33:10,363
It was my first time
seeing so many shamans ring their bells

624
00:33:10,447 --> 00:33:12,240
and connect with their deities.

625
00:33:20,582 --> 00:33:23,293
The air suddenly changed.

626
00:33:23,376 --> 00:33:25,837
I felt overwhelmed as soon as
I saw it happening.

627
00:33:26,922 --> 00:33:29,674
What is this?
Is this real or is this a dream?

628
00:33:58,328 --> 00:33:59,913
Help us see things clearly.

629
00:33:59,996 --> 00:34:01,957
Let my eyes see visions
and my tongue speak the truth.

630
00:34:02,040 --> 00:34:04,251
Help me speak with grace.

631
00:34:04,334 --> 00:34:06,753
May my deity's name
be known to more people.

632
00:34:07,837 --> 00:34:08,880
I pray.

633
00:34:28,775 --> 00:34:30,944
There are crystal balls and chairs.

634
00:34:31,987 --> 00:34:33,697
What? Seats are on the floor.

635
00:34:33,780 --> 00:34:35,991
What?
They switched up the concept.

636
00:34:36,074 --> 00:34:38,243
It finally begins.

637
00:34:40,662 --> 00:34:42,998
Be careful.
Do you need help with your bag?

638
00:34:49,713 --> 00:34:51,881
He took off his TV mask.

639
00:34:51,965 --> 00:34:54,884
- The TV mask.
- Finally, no more TV.

640
00:34:54,968 --> 00:34:57,554
Oh, dear.

641
00:35:08,356 --> 00:35:13,028
Look at Sobin's crystal ball.
I should've brought something like that.

642
00:35:16,031 --> 00:35:17,657
That knife… What…

643
00:35:18,408 --> 00:35:20,910
Isn't it uncool to stand
a knife up like that?

644
00:35:20,994 --> 00:35:23,913
Hey, it's facing me. Are you…

645
00:35:24,539 --> 00:35:27,500
Are you cursing me? I knew it.

646
00:35:28,084 --> 00:35:29,085
Happy now?

647
00:35:31,713 --> 00:35:33,381
Those with laptops
must be saju readers.

648
00:35:34,549 --> 00:35:37,302
They look so fancy
with their laptops.

649
00:35:37,385 --> 00:35:41,598
Seeing all this is
just incredible. That's all I can say.

650
00:35:41,681 --> 00:35:43,767
I've been
in entertainment for 20 years,

651
00:35:43,850 --> 00:35:46,061
but I've never seen
anything like this.

652
00:35:46,144 --> 00:35:48,271
Now it really feels like
a survival show.

653
00:35:51,858 --> 00:35:56,196
Now, it's time to introduce
the 5 Fate Reapers

654
00:35:56,905 --> 00:35:59,866
who will join you on Battle of Fates.

655
00:35:59,949 --> 00:36:00,992
Five will join?

656
00:36:01,076 --> 00:36:02,577
"Fate Reapers"?

657
00:36:03,745 --> 00:36:05,914
They're here.
What's happening?

658
00:36:07,999 --> 00:36:09,584
The doors are opening.

659
00:36:11,378 --> 00:36:13,880
- What's this?
- "Fate Reapers."

660
00:36:15,590 --> 00:36:18,677
- What's this?
- What is it? Who are they?

661
00:36:22,722 --> 00:36:26,142
With white smoke everywhere,
they really looked like the Grim Reapers.

662
00:36:27,060 --> 00:36:30,271
- "They're here to get me."
- Who are they?

663
00:36:30,355 --> 00:36:32,857
What's going on?

664
00:36:38,321 --> 00:36:39,614
Wow.

665
00:36:40,115 --> 00:36:41,116
Jeon Hyunmoo.

666
00:36:41,199 --> 00:36:42,492
JEON HYUNMOO
FATE REAPER

667
00:36:42,575 --> 00:36:43,576
Park Narae.

668
00:36:43,660 --> 00:36:45,412
PARK NARAE
FATE REAPER

669
00:36:45,495 --> 00:36:47,288
That's a killer outfit.

670
00:36:47,372 --> 00:36:49,374
She could be one of us.

671
00:36:50,083 --> 00:36:51,292
Shindong.

672
00:36:51,376 --> 00:36:52,377
SHINDONG
FATE REAPER

673
00:36:54,295 --> 00:36:57,674
I'm a die-hard SUPER JUNIOR fan.

674
00:36:57,757 --> 00:36:59,592
I'm a massive fan.

675
00:36:59,676 --> 00:37:01,678
It's such an honor to see him here.

676
00:37:02,387 --> 00:37:03,680
Lee Hosun.

677
00:37:03,763 --> 00:37:04,764
LEE HOSUN
FATE REAPER

678
00:37:04,848 --> 00:37:06,433
- From Divorce Camp.
- Oh, really?

679
00:37:06,516 --> 00:37:08,435
She's a tough one.

680
00:37:09,185 --> 00:37:10,311
Kang Jiyeong.

681
00:37:11,062 --> 00:37:13,898
I'm a survival show addict,

682
00:37:13,982 --> 00:37:16,109
so I'm a huge fan of Jiyeong's.

683
00:37:16,192 --> 00:37:19,571
I could tell at a glance
she has a dry saju.

684
00:37:19,654 --> 00:37:21,781
She's someone logical and practical.

685
00:37:21,865 --> 00:37:23,742
She seemed to have a powerful presence.

686
00:37:23,825 --> 00:37:27,912
It looked like
they gathered people with a strong aura.

687
00:37:28,580 --> 00:37:29,831
Why are they here?

688
00:37:30,749 --> 00:37:33,501
I wondered why they were here.

689
00:37:34,210 --> 00:37:37,046
They call the messengers
of the Lord of the Underworld

690
00:37:37,130 --> 00:37:39,215
the Grim Reapers.

691
00:37:39,299 --> 00:37:41,426
The 5 of us

692
00:37:41,509 --> 00:37:46,765
are Fate Reapers who were summoned
by the God of Fate.

693
00:37:48,725 --> 00:37:51,561
You'll be asked to read

694
00:37:51,644 --> 00:37:54,314
fates and truths,

695
00:37:56,149 --> 00:37:58,401
and we already know about them.

696
00:38:03,990 --> 00:38:06,409
Based on what we know,

697
00:38:06,493 --> 00:38:10,455
we will judge and decide your fate.

698
00:38:14,709 --> 00:38:16,503
This was totally unexpected.

699
00:38:16,586 --> 00:38:19,714
It meant they'd be
watching us with eagle eyes,

700
00:38:19,798 --> 00:38:21,716
which was a lot of pressure.

701
00:38:22,675 --> 00:38:25,428
I'm so excited

702
00:38:25,512 --> 00:38:27,680
and happy to be here.

703
00:38:27,764 --> 00:38:29,224
Everyone,

704
00:38:29,307 --> 00:38:30,725
give me the chills.

705
00:38:30,809 --> 00:38:32,227
I'll look forward to it.

706
00:38:32,811 --> 00:38:37,148
She seems to know a lot
about shamanism and tarot reading.

707
00:38:37,232 --> 00:38:39,859
-She's into this kind of stuff.
-Yes, I figured.

708
00:38:40,568 --> 00:38:42,403
Some of you might know,

709
00:38:42,487 --> 00:38:45,532
but my grandmother is a shaman.

710
00:38:47,534 --> 00:38:49,619
Oh, really? I had no idea.

711
00:38:50,703 --> 00:38:52,413
I'm not sure if it's true,

712
00:38:52,497 --> 00:38:54,791
but they say shamanic gifts
skip a generation,

713
00:38:54,874 --> 00:38:58,753
and people tell me I channeled it
into becoming an entertainer.

714
00:38:58,837 --> 00:39:00,797
So I think they're not so different.

715
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:04,259
They sure did gather people
that are full of spiritual energy.

716
00:39:04,342 --> 00:39:07,679
They know our work,
so I figured they'd be tough judges.

717
00:39:08,263 --> 00:39:11,015
Hello, I'm Lee Hosun, a counselor.

718
00:39:11,558 --> 00:39:13,434
In a way, I think

719
00:39:13,518 --> 00:39:16,646
you and I have something in common.

720
00:39:16,729 --> 00:39:20,233
I'll be watching closely at
how you play the role of a counselor,

721
00:39:20,316 --> 00:39:23,278
your skills, and the process.

722
00:39:23,361 --> 00:39:25,446
I felt a bit nervous
when she appeared.

723
00:39:25,530 --> 00:39:27,365
I think she'll be tough and picky.

724
00:39:28,157 --> 00:39:30,910
Sorry to say this, especially
since we've just met…

725
00:39:31,494 --> 00:39:33,997
but I don't believe in fate reading.

726
00:39:34,831 --> 00:39:36,165
I don't.

727
00:39:41,796 --> 00:39:43,882
She's tough.

728
00:39:45,466 --> 00:39:47,594
Oh. She's just like my clients.

729
00:39:48,636 --> 00:39:51,806
That was pretty uncomfortable to hear.

730
00:39:52,557 --> 00:39:54,475
I feel fired up.

731
00:39:55,810 --> 00:39:58,521
I wonder, "Is this really true?"

732
00:39:59,063 --> 00:40:02,400
"Is shamanism
something we can believe in?"

733
00:40:04,027 --> 00:40:08,281
I'll share with the viewers
only what I've seen

734
00:40:08,364 --> 00:40:10,283
and experienced myself.

735
00:40:10,366 --> 00:40:12,368
I think that's my role here.

736
00:40:12,452 --> 00:40:13,828
I'll make you believe.

737
00:40:14,454 --> 00:40:16,164
That's what our job is about.

738
00:40:16,831 --> 00:40:19,250
Korean shamanism has
a 5,000-year history.

739
00:40:19,334 --> 00:40:22,337
I'm going to show her

740
00:40:22,420 --> 00:40:25,048
how and why it's lasted so long.

741
00:40:25,673 --> 00:40:26,841
Look, they're up there.

742
00:40:27,842 --> 00:40:31,471
Oh,
they'll be watching us from up there.

743
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:33,973
The Fate Reapers added

744
00:40:34,057 --> 00:40:36,517
a whole new level of pressure.

745
00:40:38,937 --> 00:40:43,816
We'll now begin
the first round of Battle of Fates,

746
00:40:44,609 --> 00:40:46,736
the Battle of Intuition.

747
00:40:46,819 --> 00:40:48,363
BATTLE OF INTUITION

748
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:53,993
Intuition is the ability

749
00:40:54,077 --> 00:40:58,373
to sense something beyond the 5 senses,

750
00:40:58,456 --> 00:41:03,920
sight, hearing, smell, taste, and touch.

751
00:41:04,796 --> 00:41:06,130
In the Battle of Intuition,

752
00:41:06,214 --> 00:41:10,885
only 1 contestant will survive
after each question.

753
00:41:12,762 --> 00:41:15,473
The number of survivors
in the Battle of Intuition

754
00:41:15,556 --> 00:41:16,808
will be only…

755
00:41:20,353 --> 00:41:21,646
20.

756
00:41:24,148 --> 00:41:26,317
More than half of us will be gone.

757
00:41:26,859 --> 00:41:29,779
They're cutting us down to half
in the first round.

758
00:41:29,862 --> 00:41:31,823
Oh, my gosh.

759
00:41:34,701 --> 00:41:35,952
Let's have some fun.

760
00:41:38,162 --> 00:41:40,623
Here is the first question.

761
00:41:51,217 --> 00:41:53,428
What's going on?

762
00:42:01,102 --> 00:42:02,353
What's that?

763
00:42:08,317 --> 00:42:09,527
Huh, what?

764
00:42:13,698 --> 00:42:15,033
