-You can guess.

1020
00:58:15,367 --> 00:58:17,285
She died when she fell,

1021
00:58:17,369 --> 00:58:19,371
and her body was recovered later.

1022
00:58:19,955 --> 00:58:22,582
They're discussing, which means
there was more than 1 close answer.

1023
00:58:24,084 --> 00:58:26,962
I just said what I was told
and what I felt.

1024
00:58:28,130 --> 00:58:30,882
I trust my deities
and my Granny spirit.

1025
00:58:32,801 --> 00:58:34,678
I was confident.

1026
00:58:36,138 --> 00:58:39,391
Let's find out
the Fate Reapers' choice.

1027
00:58:40,225 --> 00:58:41,810
My gosh. Who's the survivor?

1028
00:58:41,893 --> 00:58:43,228
Drumroll.

1029
00:58:44,646 --> 00:58:47,023
The first survivor is…

1030
00:59:46,249 --> 00:59:48,251
Translated by Jennifer Jean Lim
